(42,	'<h1 style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\"><font size=\"4\">Sign up to receive exciting Charleston West Virginia Email News and Offers!</font></h1>\r\n<span style=\"width: 650px;\"<p align=\"justify\"><font size=\"2\">Charleston Area Hotels WV is a family of exceptional Charleston West Virginia hotels offering convenient and comfortable accommodations ideal for West Virginia vacations and travels. Sign up now for&nbsp;news from&nbsp;any one of the Hampton Inn Southridge, Charleston,&nbsp;Holiday Inn & Suites Charleston West, or Wingate&nbsp;by Wyndham, Charleston. From time to time we will send you news and information, as well as exciting email-only offers and special promotions to match your travel interests. <br />Your privacy is important to us and we will not sell, rent, or give your personal information to anyone. Please Click on the Newsletter link below to subscribe!</font></p></span>\r\n<font size=\"2\"> <!-- <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"crvs\" value=\"8NyrUvjH-z2jZFzsdmI7PfSjt_DN9IGgu1SzLFD9FEMyg6TBDIWhTWHLrn8LDhOpkLcZGQR5Mo1qezIb0BH1cMUqwHhKKpOleLWqfQrYwU03UCoP4GLo7h2aw_8mt8pM\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"redir\" value=\"http://www.discovercharlestonwv.com/eoffers_thankyou.php\" /></font>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"2\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td colspan=\"2\" align=\"left\"><font size=\"2\"><strong>Please fill out the information below</strong></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\"><font size=\"2\">Email Address</font><font color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"2\">*</font></td>\r\n            <td><font size=\"2\"><input maxlength=\"100\" size=\"40\" name=\"email\" /></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td height=\"20\" valign=\"bottom\" colspan=\"2\" align=\"left\"><font size=\"2\"><strong>Your Information</strong></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\"><font size=\"2\">First Name</font></td>\r\n           