modern art and handmade crafts in between all of the vendors makes for quite the experience!&nbsp; From gourmet food to natural and historical relics, the Capital Market is a great place to stop in or spend the day!</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Arial&quot;, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 13pt\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" align=\"middle\" width=\"600\" height=\"354\" src=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/files/20110818075022.jpg\" /></span></strong></p>',	0,	0,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	0),
