(14,	1,	'2015-06-03 14:20:30',	'2015-06-03 14:20:30',	'<div style=\"float: right; padding-left: 10px;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=zF2Ov4mSNUbs.kB_szGr2YwAo\" width=\"386\" height=\"289\"></iframe></div>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #288ea5;\">Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West</span></h3>\r\n<h4>Traveling from West</h4>\r\nI-64 East towards Charleston, take Exit 56—Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane—bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue—go straight and the Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West will be one block on your left.\r\n<h4>Traveling from East</h4>\r\nI-64 West towards Huntington, take Exit 56—Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane—bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue—go straight and the Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West will be one block on your left.\r\n<h4>Traveling from South</h4>\r\nI-77N to I-64 West, go 3 miles to Exit 56—Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane—bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue—go straight and the Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West will be one block on your left.\r\n<h4>Traveling from North</h4>\r\nI-77S/I-79S to I-64 West toward Huntington, go 4 miles to Exit 56—Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane—bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue—go straight and the Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West will be one block on your left.\r\n<h4>Traveling from Yeager Airport</h4>\r\nTake exit to airport and follow road. It will turn into Greenbrier street at intersection, stay right at intersection and follow the signs for downtown Charleston. Take I-77N/I-64 West until the two interstates split. Follow I-64, go 3 miles to Exit 56—Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane—bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue—go straight and the Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West will be one block on your left.\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #288ea5;\">Hampton Inn Charleston - Southridge</span></h3>\r\n<h4>From I-64:</h4>\r\nExit 58A Oakwood Road, turn right on 119 South, go 5 miles to Southridge Centre (on left) turn left at light on Southridge Blvd, take 1st right on Mountaineer Blvd.\r\n<h4>From Yeager Airport:</h4>\r\nTake Greenbrier Street out of Airport to I-64, West, toward Hungtinton, take Exit 58A Oakwood Rd, turn right on 119 South go 5 miles to Southridge Centre (on left) turn left at light on Southridge Blvd, take 1st right on Mountaineer Blvd.\r\n<h4>From 77 North:</h4>\r\nTake I-64 West toward Huntington, take Exit 58A Oakwood Road, turn right on 119 South, go 5 miles to Southridge Centre (on left) turn left at light on Southridge Blvd, take 1st right on Mountaineer Blvd.\r\n<h4>From 77 South:</h4>\r\nTake I-64 West toward Huntington, take Exit 58A Oakwood Rd, turn right on 119 South, go 5 miles to Southridge Centre (on left) turn left at light on Southridge Blvd, take first right on Mountaineer Blvd.\r\n<h4>From 79 South:</h4>\r\nTake I-64 West toward Huntington, take Exit 58A Oakwood Rd, turn right on 119 South, go 5 miles to Southridge Centre (on left) turn left at light on Southridge Blvd, take 1st right on Mountaineer Blvd.\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #288ea5;\">Wingate by Wyndham Charleston</span></h3>\r\n<h4>Traveling from North</h4>\r\nI-77S/I-79S to I-64 West toward Huntington, go 4 miles to Exit 56—Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane—bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue—go straight and the Wingate will be one block on your left.\r\n<h4>Traveling from South</h4>\r\nI-77N to I-64 West, go 3 miles to Exit 56—Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane—bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue—go straight and the Wingate will be one block on your left.\r\n<h4>Traveling from East</h4>\r\nI-64 West towards Huntington, take Exit 56—Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane—bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue—go straight and the Wingate will be one block on your left.\r\n<h4>Traveling from West</h4>\r\nI-64 East towards Charleston, take Exit 56—Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane—bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue—go straight and the Wingate will be one block on your left.\r\n<h4>Traveling from Yeager Airport</h4>\r\nTake exit to airport and follow road. It will turn into Greenbrier street at intersection, stay right at intersection and follow the signs for downtown Charleston. Take I-77N/I-64 West until the two intestates split. Follow I-64, go 3 miles to Exit 56—Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane—bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue—go straight and the Wingate will be one block on your left.',	'Getting Here',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'getting-here',	'',	'',	'2015-06-29 15:22:44',	'2015-06-29 19:22:44',	'',	0,	'http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/?page_id=14',	0,	'page',	'',	0),
