(194,	3,	'2015-06-30 08:30:35',	'2015-06-30 12:30:35',	'<div class=\"content-block col-3-cb\">\r\n<h4>Best Events</h4>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_297\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"210\"]<img class=\"wp-image-297\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/shutterstock_173318291-300x191.jpg\" alt=\"BBall through hoop\" width=\"210\" height=\"134\" /> WVSSAC Basketball Tournament[/caption]\r\n<h3>Annual Charleston Public Courts Tennis Tournament</h3>\r\nJuly 10-18, 2015\r\n\r\nLargest annual tennis tournament in Charleston. The public courts tournament matches take place at Schoenbaum Tennis Complex, Tennis Indoor Center and Charleston Catholic High\r\nSchool Sports Complex. rain sites include tennis indoor center, YMCA and the Charleston Tennis Club.\r\n<h3>WVSSAC Tournaments</h3>\r\nThe West Virginia Secondary School Athletic Commission (WVSSAC) hold their annual high school boys basketball, girls basketball, volleyball, baseball, tennis and track and field state\r\ntournaments in the Charleston area throughout the year.\r\n\r\nBoys Basketball - March\r\nGirls Basketball - March\r\nVolleyball - November\r\nBaseball - June\r\nTennis - April\r\nTrack and Field - April\r\n<h3>Sportsfest Meets WV Games</h3>\r\nSportsFEST includes the Jet Ski Hyrdo-Turf National Championship and the EVP Pro Am Beach Championship. WV Games, the largest collection of sanctioned sporting events in West Virginia, includes events such as a cornhole tournament, crossfit, tabata bootcamp, slalom skateboarding, wrestling, Jiu Jitsu and the West Virginia Storm will be stunting and tumbling. In total, more than 400 professional athletes will compete this weekend.\r\n<h3>Capital City Challenge</h3>\r\nSeptember 19, 2015\r\n\r\n4.2 mile Run, 4.2 mile Row, 16.8 mile Ride\r\n\r\nRun, Row &amp; Ride through the capital city on this flat, fast course that showcases the beauty of downtown Charleston. This unique yet competitive event is designed for competitors of all fitness and skill levels. This family-friendly challenge features a post-race picnic with music, kids\' activities, and great prizes. Solo and team entries are welcome.\r\n<h4>Best Time of the Year</h4>\r\nThere\'s always opportunities to watch and participate in sports in the Charleston area! Outdoor events are primarily available in late spring to early fall.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"content-block col-container-cb\">\r\n<h2>There’s a lot of great competition in Charleston! Whether you’re a spectator or a competitor,check out these great opportunities in all kinds of different sports.</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content-block col-1-cb\">\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1212 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/DC_Button_A.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />WV Power</h3>\r\nMinor League baseball team in the South Atlantic League. The Class A Pittsburgh Pirates affiliate plays home games at Appalachian Power Park, also home to the WVSSAC baseball tournament.\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">Appalachian Power Park\r\n601 Morris St.\r\nCharleston, WV 25301\r\n<a href=\"http://wvpower.com\" target=\"_blank\">wvpower.com</a></p>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/see-do/sports-fan\" target=\"_blank\"><button style=\"font-family: \'roboto_slabbold\';\">SHARE</button></a>\r\n\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1229 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/DC_Button_9-C.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />WV Chaos</h3>\r\nFounded in 2003, WV Chaos plays in the USL Premier Development League (PDL), the 4th tier of the American Soccer Pyramid, in the South Atlantic Division of the Eastern Conference.\r\n\r\nSchoenbaum Soccer Complex\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">2000 Coonskin Dr.\r\nCharleston, WV 25311\r\n<a href=\"http://westvirginiachaossoccer.com\" target=\"_blank\">westvirginiachaossoccer.com</a></p>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/see-do/sports-fan\" target=\"_blank\"><button style=\"font-family: \'roboto_slabbold\';\">SHARE</button></a>\r\n\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1233 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/DC_Button_9-E.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />University of Charleston            Athletics</h3>\r\nThe UC Golden Eagles teams consist of baseball, basketball, cross country, football, golf ,soccer, tennis, track and field, volleyball, cheerleading, rowing, lacrosse and softball.\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">University of Charleston\r\n2300 MacCorkle Ave., SE\r\nCharleston, WV 25304</p>\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">UC Stadium - Laidley Field\r\n200 Elizabeth St.\r\nCharleston, WV 25311\r\n<a href=\"http://ucgoldeneagles.com\" target=\"_blank\">ucgoldeneagles.com</a></p>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/see-do/sports-fan\" target=\"_blank\"><button style=\"font-family: \'roboto_slabbold\';\">SHARE</button></a>\r\n\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1230 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/DC_Button_9-G.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />West Virginia State                        University Athletics</h3>\r\nThe WVSU Yellow Jackets teams consist of baseball, basketball, football, golf, tennis, softball, cross country and volleyball.\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">500 Fairlawn Ave.\r\nInstitute, WV 25112\r\n<a href=\"http://www.wvsuyellowjackets.com\" target=\"_blank\">wvsuyellowjackets.com</a></p>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/see-do/sports-fan\" target=\"_blank\"><button style=\"font-family: \'roboto_slabbold\';\">SHARE</button></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"content-block col-2-cb\">\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1232 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/DC_Button_9-B.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Charleston Civic Center</h3>\r\nHosts a variety of annual sporting events including WVSSAC Boys and Girls Basketball State Tournaments, archery and volleyball tournaments, Mountain East Conference Championships, boxing/martial arts events, Capital Classic between WVU and Marshall Men\'s Basketball.\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">200 Civic Center Dr.\r\nCharleston, WV 25301\r\n<a href=\"http://www.charlestonwvciviccenter.com\" target=\"_blank\">charlestonwvciviccenter.com</a></p>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/see-do/sports-fan\" target=\"_blank\"><button style=\"font-family: \'roboto_slabbold\';\">SHARE</button></a>\r\n\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1234 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/DC_Button_9-D.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Trace Fork Soccer Complex</h3>\r\nThe Friends of Coal Fields At Trace Fork Soccer Complex is a six field soccer complex is located at the Shops at Trace Fork, just off U.S. Rt. 119 south of Charleston, West Virginia.\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">25 RHL Blvd.\r\nSouth Charleston, WV 25309\r\n<a href=\"http://traceforksoccer.com/\" target=\"_blank\">traceforksoccer.com</a></p>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/see-do/sports-fan\" target=\"_blank\"><button style=\"font-family: \'roboto_slabbold\';\">SHARE</button></a>\r\n\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1236 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/DC_Button_9-F.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Adelphia Sports Bar and              Grille</h3>\r\nVoted best appetizer and wings in the valley three years in a row! Adelphia infuses Greek and American cuisine to offer some of the best food around. Open 365 days a year and full menu served until midnight and later.\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">218 Capitol Street\r\nCharleston WV, 25301\r\n<a href=\"http://adelphiasportsbar.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://adelphiasportsbar.com/</a></p>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/see-do/sports-fan\" target=\"_blank\"><button style=\"font-family: \'roboto_slabbold\';\">SHARE</button></a>\r\n\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1231 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/DC_Button_9-H.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />South Charleston Memorial         Ice Arena</h3>\r\nNewly opened, state-of-the-art facility with amenities like an arcade and heated seating area that will accommodate 500 spectators. Groups of all sizes are welcome.\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">20 RHL Blvd.\r\nCharleston, WV 25309\r\n<a href=\"http://cityofsouthcharleston.com/memorial-ice-arena/\" target=\"_blank\">memorial-ice-arena/</a></p>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/see-do/sports-fan\" target=\"_blank\"><button style=\"font-family: \'roboto_slabbold\';\">SHARE</button></a>\r\n\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1235 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/DC_Button_9-I.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Little Creek Park</h3>\r\nThe park has five baseball/softball fields, seven soccer fields, a football field, two tennis courts and two basketball courts. Also, 18-hold disc golf course and soap box derby track are located at the park.\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">1 Little Creek Park Rd.\r\nSouth Charleston, WV 25309\r\n<a href=\"http://cityofsouthcharleston.com/little-creek-park/\" target=\"_blank\">little-creek-park/</a></p>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/see-do/sports-fan\" target=\"_blank\"><button style=\"font-family: \'roboto_slabbold\';\">SHARE</button></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n<div><iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=zF2Ov4mSNUbs.kjg5elzGTzXs\" width=\"460\" height=\"325\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>',	'Sports Fan',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'sports-fan',	'',	'',	'2015-08-17 15:40:15',	'2015-08-17 19:40:15',	'',	8,	'http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/?page_id=194',	0,	'page',	'',	0),
