mage-1227 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/DC_Button_6-D1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />B&amp;D Gastropub</h3>\r\nThe extensive menu includes appetizers such as jerk chicken nachos &amp; feta and dates wrapped in bacon. The menu will also offers burgers, including stuffed patties, fresh-cut chips and salads.\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">200 35th St SE #1\r\nCharleston, WV 25304\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/BandDGastropub\">facebook.com/BanDGastropub</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1222 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/DC_Button_6-F.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Copper Pint Pub</h3>\r\nCopper Pint Pub is an Irish Pub with a large selection of local and imported craft beers. Also carry a huge selection of Irish Whiskeys, Bourbons and Scotches to satisfy the most diverse taste buds.\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">808 Kanawha Blvd., E\r\nCharleston, WV 25301\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CopperPintPub\" target=\"_blank\">facebook.com/CopperPintPub</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n<div><iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=zF2Ov4mSNUbs.kur60CGq-7mc\" width=\"460\" height=\"345\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>',	'Brew Enthusiast',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'198-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-07-30 15:07:30',	'2015-07-30 19:07:30',	'',	198,	'http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/uncategorized/198-revision-v1',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
