(1470,	3,	'2015-08-19 16:19:05',	'2015-08-19 20:19:05',	'“Pierce Pettis doesn’t write mere songs, he writes literature…end to end the songwriting is brilliant…and his singing is marvelous, wry and warm.” - Sing Out. A wonderful performer and guitar player, his songs have been recorded by Dar Williams, Garth Brooks and Art Garfunkel. Come experience a true American original!',	'Woody Hawley Concert Series - Pierce Pettis',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'woody-hawley-concert-series-pierce-pettis',	'',	'',	'2015-08-19 16:19:05',	'2015-08-19 20:19:05',	'',	0,	'http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/?post_type=chronosly&#038;p=1470',	0,	'chronosly',	'',	0),
